room_title: Escape room "This One Time, in the 90s..." by Red Herring Escape Rooms in Shreveport
room_description: Your older sister has stolen your walkman! How will you EVER live without your jams? As luck would have it, your parents and sister have left the house giving you the chance to get it back. Unfortunately, if you get caught in your sister’s room one more time without her permission, your parents are going to send you away to boarding school! Can you sneak into your sister’s room and find your walkman before they get back and ship you off?
